### Hadith 4:476

*Narrated Abu Huraira:*

The Prophet said, "The first batch (of people) who will enter Paradise
will be (glittering) like the full moon, and the batch next to them will
be (glittering) like the most brilliant star in the sky. Their hearts
will be as if the heart of a single man, for they will have neither
enmity nor jealousy amongst themselves; everyone will have two wives
from the houris, (who will be so beautiful, pure and transparent that)
the marrow of the bones of their legs will be seen through the bones and
the flesh."

